                            <p class=""review"" slot=""content"">The conclusion to a ten year epic, Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows - Part 2 is not only suitably action-packed, but also an incredibly emotional and almost tear jerking conclusion to one of the greatest movie series&#39; ever.</p>
